### Cal.com Request for Credential Refresh

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/docs/self-hosting/guides/appstore-and-integration/syncing-third-party-apps.mdx

This JSON structure outlines the payload Cal.com sends when it needs to refresh app credentials. Your platform will receive this request at the `CALCOM_CREDENTIAL_SYNC_ENDPOINT`.

```json
{
  calcomUserId: string;
  // App slug on Cal.com
  appSlug: string;
}
```

